00:47:28.950 --> 00:47:32.380
Yeah, you're right.

00:47:47.130 --> 00:47:52.330 line:50 %
"Welcome to Cherry Park Lane"

00:48:10.020 --> 00:48:12.660
Mako?

00:48:12.660 --> 00:48:16.330
I'm sorry to have you come
out to a place like this

00:48:16.330 --> 00:48:18.700
on Christmas Eve.

00:48:18.700 --> 00:48:22.670
No, it's all right.

00:48:22.670 --> 00:48:24.700
I need a favor.

00:48:24.700 --> 00:48:26.040
Hold on a second!

00:48:26.040 --> 00:48:29.540
I have no intention of racing you.

00:48:29.540 --> 00:48:31.210
That's not it.

00:48:31.210 --> 00:48:34.340
I want you to sit next to me.

00:48:34.340 --> 00:48:36.040
What?

00:48:43.390 --> 00:48:48.590
<i>I usually have Sayuki sitting next to me.</i>

00:48:48.590 --> 00:48:50.530
<i>This feels strange.</i>

00:48:52.430 --> 00:48:54.760
Okay, here we go.

00:49:26.930 --> 00:49:29.100
<i>She's good... no, amazing!</i>

00:49:29.100 --> 00:49:31.090
<i>I had no idea.</i>

00:49:49.090 --> 00:49:52.120
You're way better than I thought you were.

00:49:52.120 --> 00:49:55.860
Very few Night Kids can drive like that.

00:49:55.860 --> 00:49:59.760
You may even be better
than Takeshi and Shingo.

00:50:02.270 --> 00:50:06.830
I think I understand why
you had me ride with you.

00:50:08.470 --> 00:50:11.500
This is your answer, isn't it?

00:50:12.680 --> 00:50:14.180
I'm sorry.

00:50:14.180 --> 00:50:16.940
I thought about it long and hard.

00:50:18.480 --> 00:50:21.650
You may think I'm a foolish girl,

00:50:21.650 --> 00:50:25.210
but I can't shake my desire for racing.

00:50:30.560 --> 00:50:34.500
I want to keep chasing after the people

00:50:34.500 --> 00:50:36.400
who are running in front of me.

00:50:37.570 --> 00:50:39.470
Even if I can't catch up with them for now,

00:50:39.470 --> 00:50:42.730
I want to keep facing the same direction.

00:50:43.970 --> 00:50:45.740
I'm so sorry.

00:50:45.740 --> 00:50:49.340
I really was very flattered.

00:50:51.750 --> 00:50:53.410
I understand.

00:50:55.590 --> 00:50:57.420
Goodbye.

00:51:12.570 --> 00:51:15.410
<i>I don't know who they are,</i>

00:51:15.410 --> 00:51:17.910
<i>but I'm so jealous</i>

00:51:17.910 --> 00:51:21.670
<i>of the people she cares about right now.</i>

00:51:28.450 --> 00:51:31.590
Hey, where's Takumi?

00:51:31.590 --> 00:51:34.260
Maybe he has a date.

00:51:34.260 --> 00:51:38.030
